---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---
<Base
  title="1:1 Coaching — Body by Olga"
  description="1:1 coaching with Olga — personalized strength training, nutrition strategy, and behavior change support for women 40+ who want deeper accountability."
  canonical="/coaching"
>
  <Nav />

  <section class="ch">
    <div class="ctn">
      <h1 class="r">For Women Who Want More Hands-On Support</h1>
      <p class="r d1">Some women do great with the app alone. Some do better with personalized guidance, deeper accountability, and a closer coaching relationship.</p>
      <p class="note r d2">If you want that level of support, this is the next step.</p>
      <a href="#" class="btn r d3">Apply for 1:1 Coaching</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="frame sp">
    <div class="ctn">
      <div class="frame-in r">
        <h2>This isn't information you're missing.</h2>
        <p>Most women who come to coaching already know what they should be doing. They've read the books. They've tried the programs.</p>
        <p>The problem is never knowledge. It's the patterns underneath — the emotional eating, the all-or-nothing thinking, the shame loops that make consistency feel impossible.</p>
        <p>Coaching is where we address that directly. Not with motivation speeches. With real tools, honest feedback, and a plan built around your actual life.</p>
        <p class="em">"The goal is not to get you fired up for a day. It's to help you build repeatable behaviors."</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="sp">
    <div class="ctn">
      <div class="cw">
        <h2 class="r">Coaching is for women who want...</h2>
        <div class="cw-g">
          <div class="cw-c r">
            <h4>More personalization</h4>
            <p>Training and nutrition adjusted to your body, your schedule, your history. Not a template.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cw-c r d1">
            <h4>More accountability</h4>
            <p>Regular check-ins with someone who knows your situation and won't let you disappear.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cw-c r d2">
            <h4>Deeper habit support</h4>
            <p>Help with emotional eating, stress responses, and the patterns that keep showing up no matter what plan you follow.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cw-c r d3">
            <h4>A closer coaching relationship</h4>
            <p>Someone who understands the problem fast, tells the truth without drama, and helps you move forward.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="chow sp">
    <div class="ctn">
      <h2 class="r">What Coaching Includes</h2>
      <div class="chow-g">
        <div class="chow-c r">
          <div class="num">01</div>
          <h4>Personalized Strength Plan</h4>
          <p>Custom programming based on your level, equipment, and goals. Adjusted as you progress.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="chow-c r d1">
          <div class="num">02</div>
          <h4>Nutrition Strategy</h4>
          <p>Food awareness work built around your real life — not calorie tracking, not rigid meal plans. Hunger skills, satiety, and better food decisions.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="chow-c r d2">
          <div class="num">03</div>
          <h4>Mindset & Behavior Coaching</h4>
          <p>We address perfectionism, emotional eating triggers, self-sabotage, and the "I blew it" cycle. Practical tools, not vague positivity.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="chow-c r d3">
          <div class="num">04</div>
          <h4>Regular Check-Ins With Olga</h4>
          <p>Consistent support, honest feedback, and adjustments as your life and body change. You're not doing this alone.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="sp">
    <div class="ctn">
      <div class="ct">
        <h2 class="r">Coaching Results</h2>
        <div class="ct-g">
          <div class="ct-c r">
            <p class="ct-q">"Olga helped me see patterns I couldn't see on my own. The emotional eating triggers were so obvious once she pointed them out."</p>
            <p class="ct-a">Bonniejean, 54</p>
            <p class="ct-d">Coaching client</p>
          </div>
          <div class="ct-c r d1">
            <p class="ct-q">"For the first time in 20 years, I have a real relationship with food. Not a diet. A relationship. That shift changed everything."</p>
            <p class="ct-a">Mika, 47</p>
            <p class="ct-d">Coaching client</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cf sp">
    <div class="ctn">
      <div class="r">
        <h2>Let's find a way that<br>actually works for you.</h2>
        <p>No pressure. Just a conversation.</p>
        <a href="#" class="btn">Apply for 1:1 Coaching</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Base>
